<img style="margin-top: -30px; margin-bottom: 10px;" width="300" data-src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/black.jpg" class=" ls-is-cached lazyloaded" src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/black.jpg" loading="lazy"><noscript><img style="margin-top: -30px; margin-bottom: 10px;" src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/black.jpg" width="300"></noscript>
<br>
<p>Creating meaningful emotional connections with your audience is essential for your company to stand out. <br><br>
We act as a strategic partner in the corporate video production process to enable you to communicate your message effectively so that it resonates with your target audience and leaves a lasting impact. Our method is always customized, creative, and most importantly, results-driven. </p>

<p><br>Here’s a quick rundown of how our corporate video production process works:</p>
</div></div></div></div><div class="wrap mcb-wrap one  valign-top clearfix" style=""><div class="mcb-wrap-inner"><div class="column mcb-column one column_content "><div class="the_content"><div class="the_content_wrapper"><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="cq-expandgrid cq-circular- cq-expandgrid-200 cq-expandgrid-avatar-200 cq-expandgrid-close-yes cq-expandgrid-in5  " data-itemheight="" data-autoslide="5" data-itemsize="200" data-transparentitem="yes" data-openfirst="" data-labelfontsize="" data-nocircular="" data-subfontsize=""><div class="cq-expandgrid-item cq-transparent cq-expandgrid-openstate" data-image="" data-bgstyle="cq-transparent" data-backgroundcolor="" data-backgroundhovercolor="" data-avatartype="image" data-avatar="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1.png" data-contentcolor="" data-iconcolor="" data-iconsize="" data-labelcolor="" data-subtitlecolor="" title=""><div class="cq-expandgrid-face cq-expandgrid-toggle"><div class="cq-expandgrid-facecontent"><div class="cq-expandgrid-avatar" style="background-image: url(&quot;https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1.png&quot;);"></div></div></div><div class="cq-expandgrid-content"><div class="cq-expandgrid-text"><p><img style="margin-left: 10%;" width="80" data-src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/arrow-4-1.png" class=" ls-is-cached lazyloaded" src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/arrow-4-1.png" loading="lazy"><noscript><img style="margin-left: 10%;" src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/arrow-4-1.png" width="80" /></noscript></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400; color: #000;">It’s absolutely critical you know what you want to achieve with your video outreach efforts. After all, if you don’t have goals, how do you measure your success? If you’re unsure about your project objectives, we’ll figure them out together so we can craft a meaningful story. </span></p>
<hr>
</div><i class="fa fa-close cq-expandgrid-close"></i></div></div><div class="cq-expandgrid-item cq-transparent cq-expandgrid-initstate outfoucs" data-image="" data-bgstyle="cq-transparent" data-backgroundcolor="" data-backgroundhovercolor="" data-avatartype="image" data-avatar="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2.png" data-contentcolor="" data-iconcolor="" data-iconsize="" data-labelcolor="" data-subtitlecolor="" title=""><div class="cq-expandgrid-face cq-expandgrid-toggle"><div class="cq-expandgrid-facecontent"><div class="cq-expandgrid-avatar" style="background-image: url(&quot;https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2.png&quot;);"></div></div></div><div class="cq-expandgrid-content"><div class="cq-expandgrid-text"><p><img style="margin-left: 32%;" width="80" data-src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/arrow-4-1.png" class=" ls-is-cached lazyloaded" src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/arrow-4-1.png" loading="lazy"><noscript><img style="margin-left: 32%;" src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/arrow-4-1.png" width="80" /></noscript><br>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">Now that we know your “what,” we need to identify your “who.” So who is your target market? What do you want them to feel after watching your story? Once we figure out this information, we determine what action you want your audience to take after viewing your content. </span></p>
<hr>
</div><i class="fa fa-close cq-expandgrid-close"></i></div></div><div class="cq-expandgrid-item cq-transparent cq-expandgrid-initstate outfoucs" data-image="" data-bgstyle="cq-transparent" data-backgroundcolor="" data-backgroundhovercolor="" data-avatartype="image" data-avatar="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/3.png" data-contentcolor="" data-iconcolor="" data-iconsize="" data-labelcolor="" data-subtitlecolor="" title=""><div class="cq-expandgrid-face cq-expandgrid-toggle"><div class="cq-expandgrid-facecontent"><div class="cq-expandgrid-avatar" style="background-image: url(&quot;https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/3.png&quot;);"></div></div></div><div class="cq-expandgrid-content"><div class="cq-expandgrid-text"><p><img style="margin-left: 48%;" width="80" data-src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/striaght.png" class=" ls-is-cached lazyloaded" src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/striaght.png" loading="lazy"><noscript><img style="margin-left: 48%;" src="https://3lpbthhwasv2algbrbe0j611-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/striaght.png" width="80" /></noscript></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Next, we reverse-engineer your objectives to identify the pieces needed to reach your “destination.” In some cases, you may need multiple stories or videos for different platforms. (For instance, you can’t show the same length video on Instagram that you use on your website.). We also lay out a step-by-step strategy for distribution.</span></p>
